{id:"item-boots-of-the-winterlands",name:"Boots of the Winterlands",content:[{id:"Title",content:"Boots of the Winterlands"},{id:"Image",url:"https://www.dnd5eapi.co/api/images/magic-items/boots-of-the-winterlands.png"},{id:"StatGrid",content:[{title:"Category",content:"Wondrous Items"},{title:"Rarity",content:"Uncommon"}]},{id:"MultiText",content:["Wondrous item, uncommon (requires attunement)","These furred boots are snug and feel quite warm. While you wear them, you gain the following benefits:","* You have resistance to cold damage.","* You ignore difficult terrain created by ice or snow.","* You can tolerate temperatures as low as -50 degrees Fahrenheit without any additional protection. If you wear heavy clothes, you can tolerate temperatures as low as -100 degrees Fahrenheit."]}]}